Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.61,0:24:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}塔奇克马式的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.00,0:24:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是干什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.10,0:24:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是 睡着了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.99,0:24:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会不会
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.28,0:24:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么说明…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.03,0:24:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.73,0:24:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是保持距离比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.71,0:24:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.00,0:24:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像踩到什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.24,0:24:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.18,0:25:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么开关？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.46,0:25:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RESET THE WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.01,0:25:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.10,0:25:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.55,0:25:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快顶住


